&lt;p&gt;BUILD FAILED&lt;br/&gt;
/root/hive/build.xml:179: /root/hive/service/lib/php not found.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Total time: 15 seconds&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;When I manually created the directory, it goes through, but a bunch of files are missing. For example, fb303_types.php.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
